                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18041205-28-defend376 t18041205-28-punish166"></join>
               fined 1 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Grose.</p>
